

?panx-framework v0.2.4
---------------------

?This is next release of panx-framework (v0.2.4). This is major version release.

?The documentation is available on https://panx.eu/docs/.
!(In future, it will available only using https://panx.eu/docs/v0.2.4/)

?New features
- Fixed bugs.
- Added 2FA
- Displaying recaptcha after failed login etc.
- Added _ga() - Google Analytics
- Logging accesses
- Previous URL remember
- dump() with no param
- n:link (Route aliases)
- Logging visits with username

?After installation
After installation, you need to run following commands:
?composer install
?php panx-worker config

?If you want to use Authentification, you should download Auth extension with template files, routes, css, imgs, fonts by running following command:
?php panx-worker extension install https://panx.eu/download/extensions/Auth.zip

